# .env.staging
# SEKAR Mobile — STAGING / UAT (deployed AWS API over plain HTTP)
#
# Activate with the ENVFILE switch (babel.config.js reads process.env.ENVFILE):
#   ENVFILE=.env.staging npm start -- --reset-cache
#   ENVFILE=.env.staging npm run android
#
# Values are inlined at bundle time — ALWAYS --reset-cache after switching.

